# Security

## Authentication
- I am adding authentication because:
  - User identity verification is needed

## Authorization
- I am adding authorization because:
  - Access control is required

## Encryption
- I am encrypting data because:
  - Security in transit and at rest is important

## WAF
- I am adding a Web Application Firewall because:
  - Protection against common attacks

---

# High Traffic / Celebrity Problems

## Hot Keys
- I am handling hot keys using:
  - Replication
  - Caching
  - Request spreading

## Request Coalescing
- I am using request collapsing because:
  - Multiple identical requests hit backend once

## Precomputation
- I am precomputing feeds/results because:
  - Reduces expensive read-time computation

---

# Microservices

## Service Discovery
- I am adding service discovery because:
  - Services should dynamically locate each other

## Config Management
- I am externalizing configuration because:
  - Easier deployments
  - Better environment management

## Sidecar Pattern
- I am using sidecars because:
  - Handles observability/security separately

---

# Data Processing

## Batch Processing
- I am using batch processing because:
  - Large-scale offline computation is needed

## Stream Processing
- I am using stream processing because:
  - Near real-time processing is required

## CDC (Change Data Capture)
- I am using CDC because:
  - DB changes should propagate asynchronously

