# System Design Closing Statements

## Tradeoff
- This design optimizes for:
  - Scalability
  - Availability

- While accepting:
  - Eventual consistency tradeoffs

## MVP
- For MVP:
  - I would keep the design simpler
  - Add complexity gradually as scale grows

## Future Improvements
- Future optimizations can include:
  - Better caching
  - Smarter partitioning
  - Multi-region deployment
